  <!-- EN: 【First-rate】Oblivion soul-purging elixir -->
  <RI_Drug_OblivionSoulPurgingElixir.label>【一品】湮尘忘魂丹</RI_Drug_OblivionSoulPurgingElixir.label>
  <!-- EN: "The primordial celestial immortals spent countless years in arduous contemplation, creating the Nine Primal Initial Approach. However, as their strength waned, they transmuted the remnants of their surroundings into a pill to erase their own knowledge, thus naming it the Soul-Purging Elixir. ——Records of the Celestial Immortals\n\nThis is a most enigmatic and wondrous elixir, its formula personally passed down by the immortals and unchanged through millennia. Only those with unwavering resolve, truly willing to abandon the Initial Approach they have mastered, can experience its effects. Should doubt linger in their hearts, the pill will be powerless, and the Initial Approach shall remain. -->
  <RI_Drug_OblivionSoulPurgingElixir.description>“相传，原始天仙苦心悟道多年，发明九大法门。之后消耗过大，以身边所剩不多之物，点化为忘魂丹，用于遗忘法门。“——《天仙记》\n\n这是一种玄而又玄的奇妙丹药，其配方乃是天仙亲自流传，在千年长河中并未更改。服用丹药之人，必须一心求变，彻底抛弃法门，否则丹药便无效果。</RI_Drug_OblivionSoulPurgingElixir.description>
  <!-- EN: 服用 {0} -->
  <RI_Drug_OblivionSoulPurgingElixir.ingestible.ingestCommandString>服用 {0}</RI_Drug_OblivionSoulPurgingElixir.ingestible.ingestCommandString>
