  <!-- EN: 【Second-rate】QiLin restoration pill -->
  <RI_Drug_QiLinRestorationPill.label>【二品】麒麟丸</RI_Drug_QiLinRestorationPill.label>
  <!-- EN: Second-rate Elixir，The QiLin restoration pill is a pale green pill with a subtle bamboo fragrance. It is refined from the most healing ingredients, capable of healing skin scars and mildly enhancing the body's natural healing abilities. -->
  <RI_Drug_QiLinRestorationPill.description>麒麟丸是一种外形淡绿色的药丸，闻上去有丝丝竹香。这种药丸以最具治愈效果的药材精炼而成，能治愈皮肤的伤疤，还能轻微提升人体自身的愈合能力。</RI_Drug_QiLinRestorationPill.description>
